{"tid":1923539,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港基本人權排名急跌五位","createTime":"2020-03-13T06:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T07:53:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2f6707e8b40f72aa493a1cf67585a77c3d436c","tid":1923539,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200313/DYKMH6SLFAFFCDR4OJO6MC6O4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200313%2FDYKMH6SLFAFFCDR4OJO6MC6O4A%2F&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCbc0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=624ba40e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200313%2FDYKMH6SLFAFFCDR4OJO6MC6O4A%2F&h=625b2a0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200313/DYKMH6SLFAFFCDR4OJO6MC6O4A/</a><br />\n<br />\n港基本人權排名急跌五位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200313/large/1584030786_6232.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200313%2Flarge%2F1584030786_6232.jpg&h=0e8b8e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港基本人權排名大幅下跌。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「世界正義工程」（World Justice Project，WJP）公佈2020年「法治指數」排名，香港維持在東亞及太平洋地區第5位、世界排名第16位；但在「基本人權」的全球排名則下跌五位至第38位；本港「落實法規」方面的全球排名亦下跌兩位至第12位，兩者表現均遜新加坡。<br />\n<br />\n世界正義工程是國際公民組織，其「法治指數」為衡量國家或地方堅持實踐法治的程度，該指數由八個分項指數組成，包括政府權力的制約、廉潔度、開放政府、基本權利、社會秩序和安全等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港府指社會情緒影響<br />\n<br />\n香港今年的「法治指數」在128個國家或司法管轄區中排名16，整體法治得0.76分（最高1分、最低0分），比去年微跌0.01分。但在八個分項評分當中，香港在「政府權力的制約」及「基本人權」表現最差，排名分別第31及38位，其中後者排名由去年33位跌至今年38位；「廉潔」、「秩序與安全」、「民事司法」和「刑事司法」排名則均有上升。<br />\n<br />\n政府昨晚發聲明，特別指出在「秩序與安全」範疇排名上升兩位至第2位，並指香港的整體罪案情況連續12年呈下跌趨勢，但港府未提及「基本人權」排名急跌，並稱「我們承認社會上的情緒可能影響公眾和部份國際社會對香港法治的看法」，及強調香港穩固的法治基礎仍然完好無損。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁穎妍"},{"pid":"945bf2b8339d487f943a0cfa94ce73e299b7e321","tid":1923539,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T06:40:33.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51377e1af5b25cf1674ff552728d27ec1224b510","tid":1923539,"uid":198214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f5ba3fff5823b41411f1aa04f5e204cf2bbb2adb","tid":1923539,"uid":76365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T06:47:22.000Z","msg":"喂個法治指數係想點<br />\n定因為2019冇依家咁多法治屍體？"},{"pid":"21444129318519c15cfdf79410e4767a639fe894","tid":1923539,"uid":76365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"秩序與安全上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb45f8b557b97fe301ed0ad25f1189933b42ea36","tid":1923539,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T06:51:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1438e46b7719f3053d4527331c2cd0f020175cb8","tid":1923539,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T06:51:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"caad71450ac52849637d034007499b4b919f9193","tid":1923539,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:53:02.000Z","msg":"林鄭點孭得起呢個罪名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}